// Basic interface to "Ballistic" kernel
// ================================================

OP 1 - "To freeze ..."
  trig:   
    DO[ fcn-1 -lex-  freeze 
              -fcn-> act-1 ] 
---------------
   GND[ call-1 -lex-  ball_stop 
               -arg-> act-1 ]


